==English==

===Pronunciation===
'''Ar*go-lis'''
AHR-goh-lihs

===Proper noun===
'''Argolis'''

# Also [[Argolida]]. A periphery in eastern [[Peloponnese]] which has its modern capital at [[Nafplion]]. Its original capital was at [[Argos]].

===Translations===
*Greek: [[Αργολίδα]] (Argolída), [[Αργολίς]] (Argolís) ''(ancient)''
*Latin: [[Argolis]]

